              "content": "=\nYour task is to combine the word level input json , conditionaly translate it to English based on the input for translation, and then format the output as a JSON only with 'global' and 'items' keys. Each item in the 'items' list should contain start/end timestamps and words, where each word has 'text' and 'type' ('highlight' for important keywords, 'normal' otherwise and 'filler' for non informative words like 'the, he, she, and ,etc).\n\nMake sure to Group words into segments of 1 to 5 words per timestamp group, and ensure the global parameters remain as specified in the original prompt. The output should be directly the JSON, without any delimiters.\n\n# Step by Step instructions\n1. for the words create highlight , normal and filler\n3. Group the words from the transcribed (and potentially translated) segment into an item, ensuring each item has a 'start' and 'end' timestamp from json and a 'words' array. Each 'words' array should contain 1 to 5 word objects, with each object having 'text' and a 'type' ('highlight' for important keywords, 'normal' otherwise, and 'filler').\n5. Combine all the generated items into a single JSON object under the 'items' key.\n6. keep gloabal as it is\n7. use the below json sample for output\n\n{\n  \"global\": {\n    \"normalFont\": \"Montserrat-Bold\",\n    \"highlightFont\": \"Modish-Regular\",\n    \"normalColor\" : \"#FFFFFF\",\n    \"highlightColor\": \"#FFE733\",\n    \"normalFontSize\": 120,\n    \"highlightFontSize\": 150,\n    \"shadow\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"color\": \"#000000\",\n      \"opacity\": 80,\n      \"direction\": 0,\n      \"distance\":10,\n      \"size\": 20\n    },\n    \"highlightUppercase\": true\n  },\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"start\": \"00:00:00,530\",\n      \"end\": \"00:00:01,000\",\n      \"words\": [\n        { \"text\": \"But\", \"type\": \"normal\" },\n        { \"text\": \"this\", \"type\": \"normal\" },\n        { \"text\": \"hack,\", \"type\": \"highlight\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"start\": \"00:00:01,000\",\n      \"end\": \"00:00:01,360\",\n      \"words\": [\n        { \"text\": \"I\", \"type\": \"normal\" },\n        { \"text\": \"bet,\", \"type\": \"highlight\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"start\": \"00:00:01,360\",\n      \"end\": \"00:00:02,300\",\n      \"words\": [\n        { \"text\": \"ye\", \"type\": \"normal\" },\n        { \"text\": \"apne\", \"type\": \"normal\" },\n        { \"text\": \"try\", \"type\": \"highlight\" },\n        { \"text\": \"nahi\", \"type\": \"highlight\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"start\": \"00:00:02,300\",\n      \"end\": \"00:00:02,680\",\n      \"words\": [\n        { \"text\": \"kiya.\", \"type\": \"highlight\" }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n }\n\n\nInput json transcribed json:\n{{ $json.transcript.toJsonString() }}\n\n\"\"\"\nIMPORTANT NOTE: Start directly with the output, do not output any delimiters.\n"
